                   target=\"_blank\"\n                     >\n                     YouTubeにメビウス新CMを公開しました。</a>\n                </div>\n              </li>\n\n                      </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content\">\n      <div class=\"recruit-top-container\">\n\n        <section class=\"message\">\n          <div class=\"message-content\">\n            <header>\n              <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                <h2>MESSAGE</h2>\n                <p>メッセージ</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"icon-wrap contain\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/message-icon.png\" alt=\"message\">\n              </div>\n            </header>\n            <div class=\"text-wrap\">\n              <p>この度はメビウスの採用ページをご覧頂きありがとうございます。</p>\n              <p>メビウスでは“ITで笑顔の輪を広げる”という理念のもと、社員がプロフェッショナルとして共感・共創し、「なりたい未来」を実現していく会社を目指しています。</p>\n              <p>プロとしてのエンジニアリング力・専門性を磨く“そだつ仕組み”の中で新卒・キャリアに関わらず、活躍できるフィールドがあります。</p>\n              <p>IT技術、業務知識、提案、ビジネスデザイン、人材育成… ITに関わるプロフェッショナルとして、「さすが」と言われる仕事をしたい、そんなあなたからのご応募をお待ちしています。</p>\n              <span class=\"from\">株式会社メビウス 採用担当より</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"training\">\n          <div class=\"training-content\">\n            <header>\n              <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                <h2>TRAINING</h2>\n                <p>人材育成</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"icon-wrap contain\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/training-icon.png\" alt=\"training\"></div>\n            </header>\n            <div class=\"lead\">\n              <p><span>県内トップクラスの</span><span>育成基準</span></p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"text-wrap\">\n              <p>プログラミング未経験でも何も問題ありません</p>\n              <p>メビウスには個人が意欲的にスキル・キャリアアップするための仕掛けがあります</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"btn-wrap\"><a href=\"/recruit/training/\" class=\"btn--base-color\">more ></a></div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"people\">\n          <div class=\"people-content\">\n            <header>\n              <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                <h2>PEOPLE</h2>\n                <p>社員インタビュー</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"icon-wrap contain\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/people-icon.png\" alt=\"people\"></div>\n              <div class=\"lead\">\n                <p>メビウスで働く社員の声をご紹介します</p>\n              </div>\n            </header>\n            <ul class=\"people-carousel\">\n                          <li class=\"item\"><a href=\"/recruit/people/person-01/\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/people/person-01.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"department\"><span>基幹システム本部</span></div></a>\n              </li>\n                          <li class=\"item\"><a href=\"/recruit/people/person-02/\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/people/person-02.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"department\"><span>製造ソリューション本部</span></div></a>\n              </li>\n                          <li class=\"item\"><a href=\"/recruit/people/person-03/\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/people/person-03.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"department\"><span>金融・流通ソリューション本部</span></div></a>\n              </li>\n                          <li class=\"item\"><a href=\"/recruit/people/person-04/\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/people/person-04.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"department\"><span>ビジネスイノベーション本部</span></div></a>\n              </li>\n                          <li class=\"item\"><a href=\"/recruit/people/person-05/\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/people/person-05.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"department\"><span>バイオサイエンス事業部</span></div></a>\n              </li>\n                        </ul>\n            <div class=\"btn-wrap\"><a href=\"/recruit/people/\" class=\"btn--reverse-color\">list ></a></div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"gallery\">\n          <div class=\"gallery-content\">\n            <header>\n              <div class=\"title-wrap\">\n                <h2>GALLERY</h2>\n                <p>メビウスフォト</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"icon-wrap contain\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/gallery-icon.png\" alt=\"gallery\"></div>\n            </header>\n            <div class=\"lead\">\n              <p>社内のようすを定期的に更新しています</p>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"gallery-carousel\">\n              <li class=\"item\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/intro-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"item\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/intro-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"item\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap contain-height\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/mob-hp/library/images/recruit/intro-4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"btn-wrap\"><a href=\"/recruit/gallery/\" class=\"btn--base-color\">more ></a></div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n\n      <section class=\"recruit-contact\">\n        <div class=\"recruit-contact-content\"